It's a book called "\rManipulating the Stock Market and You\c[0]."
Would you like to read it?
The Stock Market of the Torren Region functions like the majority of stock markets- as the value of the company goes up, so does your share!
It's technically illegal (due to the small overall population of the region), but the market can be influenced slightly by purchases.
Investing in Pokeballs before buying a lot of them is a very viable strategy!
